Package: victorgmtools
Title: Herramientas para el análisis económico y la obtención, procesamiento y visualización de datos
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Victor", "Gutiérrez Marcos", email = "contacto@victorgutierrezmarcos.es", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a collection of functions for economic data analysis, including trade balance calculations, growth rates, price indices, and real flow adjustments. Includes tools for retrieving data from FRED, handling exchange rates, and applying standardized styling to 'ggplot2' graphics and 'gt' tables.
